Manual Test Cases:

Verify the presence of input field on the home page.
Verify the presence of submit button on the home page.
Enter a valid input string in the input field and submit.
Verify that the result page is displayed after submitting the input.
Verify the correctness of the longest substring without repeating letters displayed on the result page.

Automation Test Cases:

Automate the scenario of entering a valid input string and verifying the correctness of the longest substring without repeating letters displayed on the result page.